    rdfs:comment 'Foreign key linking to customer.segment. Business justification: Marketing audience segments are operationally derived from CRM customer segments. This link enables traceability from activation audience back to the CRM segment definition, supporting segment governa' ;
    rdfs:domain ind:AudienceSegment ;
